---

<section class="hero" id="hero-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-grid">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <div class="hero-kicker-container">
                    <span class="location-badge">
                        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"></path><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle></svg>
                        Santiago, Chile
                    </span>
                    <span class="kicker" style="margin-bottom: 0;">Liderazgo, Cultura & Excelencia Técnica</span>
                </div>
                <h1 class="hero-title">Solutions Architect · Technical Lead · Senior Software Engineer</h1>
                <p class="hero-subtitle">
                    12 años diseñando y construyendo plataformas para organismos públicos, instituciones financieras y empresas privadas. Arquitectura de software, cloud, seguridad e integración de IA aplicada al desarrollo.<br><br>Disponible para incorporarme a equipos de tecnología o colaborar en proyectos.
                </p>
                <div class="hero-btns">
                    <a href="#contact-section" class="btn btn-primary">Conversemos</a>
                    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/edgardovasquezvalenzuela" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary">
                        <svg width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"/></svg>
                        LinkedIn
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-image-wrapper">
                <div class="hero-backdrop-glow"></div>
                <div class="hero-image-frame">
                    <picture>
                        <source srcset="/mpedf3pv-img.avif" type="image/avif">
                        <source srcset="/mpedf3pv-img.webp" type="image/webp">
                        <img src="/mpedf3pv-img.jpg" alt="Edgardo Vásquez Valenzuela" class="profile-img" width="320" height="400" fetchpriority="high" decoding="async">
                    </picture>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .hero-kicker-container {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .location-badge {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        padding: 4px 10px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 20px;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        white-space: nowrap;
    }
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .hero-kicker-container {
            justify-content: center;
        }
    }
</style>
